{"id":27455,"date":[{"year":1938,"month":8,"day":19}],"page":"11","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"灯塔","column":"大众信箱,问答栏:","genre":"","count":"76","ytitle":"","mtitle":"父子","ftitle":"","authors":["安之"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"安之"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲:父为汉奸，子作窃贼，父子媲美，究竟谁比较美些?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙:当然做父亲的比儿子漂亮些儿，不是吗?俗语说:“窃钩者诛，窃国者侯。”"}]}